caption: Ever wonder what goes into creating a custom logo for a business? 🤔 This video gives you a sneak peek from the spec phase for a a mural project in Clark, NJ! It's so exciting to see an idea come to life, from the supplied design to a bold statement on a building exterior.  Exterior murals are especially valuable in towns that prohibit signage in certain areas.✨ As an #njartist, I love bringing unique visions to reality. Let's collaborate and create something amazing for your business! #njmuralartist
